ts on multilingual long-horizon workplace workflows.  To enable comprehensive=
 evaluation, we propose a hybrid framework that combines structural grading, =
executable verification, and LLM-based semantic assessment.  This design allo=
ws us to capture both functional correctness and linguistic consistency acros=
s complex workflows. </p>
